    <item>
      <title>韩国反对派同意取消散户投资者税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国主要反对党将支持政府放弃对散户投资者金融投资征收资本利得税的决定，从而放弃数月来对这一有争议举措的抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/korea-s-main-opposition-backs-plan-to-drop-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 02:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“特朗普贸易”疑虑令美元承压，提振债券期货</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周二美国大选前的民意调查数据促使一些投资者削减所谓的特朗普交易，美元指数创下自 8 月底以来的最大跌幅，美国国债期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 推迟增产且伊朗加强言论，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+同意将12月份的增产计划推迟一个月且中东紧张局势再度升级，推动油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国民意调查显示没有明确领导者，美元走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元下跌，因为投资者放弃了对唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的押注，因为最新的一系列民意调查数据显示特朗普没有明显优势。OPEC+推迟增产后，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚矿业亿万富翁埃里森因涉嫌隐匿付款接受调查而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/mineral-resource-to-fine-ellison-a-8-8-milllion-to-step-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[矿产资源有限公司 (Mineral Resources Ltd.) 创始人克里斯·埃里森 (Chris Ellison) 将辞去董事总经理一职，此前对未申报付款的内部调查发现他存在“令人深感失望”的行为，该消息导致公司市值蒸发高达 8 亿澳元（5.28 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/mineral-resource-to-fine-ellison-a-8-8-milllion-to-step-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从股票到加密货币的投资者为美国大选波动做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/investors-from-stocks-to-crypto-brace-for-us-election-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在竞争激烈、胜负难分的美国大选之前，各个市场的期权交易员似乎都在降低风险，准备迎接更多波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/investors-from-stocks-to-crypto-brace-for-us-election-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
